SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT 'BEFORE1992' "TOTALTYPE", COUNT(DISTINCT bpsr_year) "TOTALDEPOSITYEARS" FROM tap_bps_register_vw01 r WHERE bpsr_ppr_id = ~1 AND bpsr_year < 1992 AND bpst_classification = 'GRDAM' UNION ALL SELECT 'IN1992' "TOTALTYPE", COUNT(DISTINCT bpsr_year) "TOTALDEPOSITYEARS" FROM tap_bps_register_vw01 r WHERE bpsr_ppr_id = ~1 AND bpsr_year = 1992 AND bpst_classification = 'GRDAM' UNION ALL SELECT 'AFTER1992' "TOTALTYPE", COUNT(DISTINCT bpsr_year) "TOTALDEPOSITYEARS" FROM tap_bps_register_vw01 r WHERE bpsr_ppr_id = ~1 AND bpsr_year BETWEEN 1993 AND ~2 AND bpst_classification = 'GRDAM'
